                   Sustainable Sourcing Framework

                    ------------------------------
                    |                          |
                    |    Environmental         |
                    |     Dimension            |
                    |                          |
                    | - Carbon footprint       |
                    |   mapping and reduction  |
                    | - Sustainable practices |
                    | - Eco-friendly          |
                    |   transportation        |
                    | - Compliance with       |
                    |   environmental         |
                    |   standards              |
                    |                          |
                    |                          |
                    |                          |
                    |                          |
                    |    Social Dimension      |
                    |                          |
                    | - Social responsibility |
                    |   and ethics             |
                    | - Codes of conduct       |
                    | - Community engagement   |
                    | - Supplier training and  |
                    |   support                |
                    |                          |
                    |                          |
                    |                          |
                    |                          |
                    |    Economic Dimension    |
                    |                          |
                    | - Total cost of          |
                    |   ownership (TCO)        |
                    | - Long-term partnerships |
                    | - Financial stability    |
                    |   and risk management    |
                    | - Sustainable sourcing  |
                    |   as a competitive       |
                    |   advantage              |
                    |                          |
                    ------------------------------
